3FE1529D.Line5.1275AB: If we are to have any chance against the cannibals, we must remember the glory of our ancestors. Those who died so that we may live.

675DA8DB.Line3.1275AB: We’ve forgotten who we are. Forgotten the sacrifices our ancestors made when faced with certain defeat. The pride of rising beyond yourself.

8ED9FF19.Line1.1275AB: It seems we’ve lost more than flesh against the cannibals.
